    - rid: 2406609200015737220
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "\rI have no problem with anyone"
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737221
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Are you sure?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737222
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Okay, maybe I have small problem with those tiny creatures.

'
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737223
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Kill those monsters! There are 3 wolves. '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737224
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: They are looking like zombies sometimes, but it might be a bug.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737225
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609200015737226
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609200015737227
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 2406609200015737228
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Leave me alone...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737229
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I'm done with fighting.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737230
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, sorry for bothering your mighty head
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737231
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hey, i've heard that you may have some problem with wolves in forest?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737232
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Did you complete the task?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737233
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Please, leave me...

'
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737234
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay great... But...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737235
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You have this great sword and you said that you won't fight anymore
          so...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737236
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: So you want my sword? If yes, just say it.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737237
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well, yes
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737238
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: There is no chance, but I can give you a wolf slayer. A spear whose
          owner was the most powerful slayer of wolf-like creatures in the forests.
          Of course, for a certain fee I can give it to you....
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737239
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Do you want "Wolf slayer spear"? '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737240
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Fuck it, give it to me. *(pay 50gp)*\r"
    - rid: 2406609200015737241
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Nah, I preferred the sword so will thank you.
    - rid: 2406609200015737242
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'I don''t have enough money...

'
    - rid: 2406609200015737243
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Wow thanks, I didn't expect you to take this worthless.... I mean magical
          and invincible spear. Returns not accepted because.... It was used. Yes,
          it was used.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737244
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Wait, but you said this weapon is...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737245
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: It is the best! Unfortunately, you have a task, and now with this weapon
          you can complete it twice as fast.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737246
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Ehhh, okay then. See you soon.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737247
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: For real? You really think that you can beat them without my mighty
          spear?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737248
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well... yes?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737249
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well, I was going to give it to you anyway
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737250
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Ohh, you poor man, I understand you. I once knew a white-haired warrior
          who was also robbed while drinking.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737251
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Good luck my friend!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737252
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: '*(you gave him 50gp)*'
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737253
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Wolves are dead
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 2406609200015737254
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Great! As promised, here are three potatoes. See you around!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
