    - id: 18
      language: en
      text: Narrator
    - id: 19
      language: en
      text: 'Do you want "Wolf slayer spear"? '
    - id: 20
      language: en
      text: "Fuck it, give it to me. *(pay 50gp)*\r"
    - id: 21
      language: en
      text: Nah, I preferred the sword so will thank you.
    - id: 22
      language: en
      text: 'I don''t have enough money...

'
    - id: 23
      language: en
      text: Wow thanks, I didn't expect you to take this worthless.... I mean magical
        and invincible spear. Returns not accepted because.... It was used. Yes,
        it was used.
    - id: 24
      language: en
      text: Wait, but you said this weapon is...
    - id: 25
      language: en
      text: It is the best! Unfortunately, you have a task, and now with this weapon
        you can complete it twice as fast.
    - id: 26
      language: en
      text: Ehhh, okay then. See you soon.
    - id: 27
      language: en
      text: For real? You really think that you can beat them without my mighty spear?
    - id: 28
      language: en
      text: Well... yes?
    - id: 29
      language: en
      text: Well, I was going to give it to you anyway
    - id: 30
      language: en
      text: Ohh, you poor man, I understand you. I once knew a white-haired warrior
        who was also robbed while drinking.
    - id: 31
      language: en
      text: Good luck my friend!
    - id: 32
      language: en
      text: '*(you gave him 50gp)*'
    - id: 33
      language: en
      text: Wolves are dead
    - id: 34
      language: en
      text: Great! As promised, here are three potatoes. See you around!
